Package lib.lists

Class CircularDoubleLinkedList<T>

java.lang.Object
lib.lists.CircularDoubleLinkedList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements stored in the list
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<T>, ListADT<T>
public class CircularDoubleLinkedList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ListADT<T>
A generic circular doubly linked list implementation that provides various operations to manage elements of the list.
